---
title: Veggie 'Nduja and Butter Bean Stew with Charred Courgette and Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Veggie 'Nduja and Butter Bean Stew in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W30_UK_QV18800-5_MAIN_high-0641865c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/664c9b73db12ba3a5e10149f-en-GB.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/veggie-nduja-and-butter-bean-stew-664c9b73db12ba3a5e10149f
author: Sam Richards
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
nutrition:
  calories: 687 kcal
  fat: 23.3 g
  saturated fat: 11.9 g
  carbohydrates: 94.4 g
  sugar: 13.4 g
  protein: 24.7 g
